OL,3,CMurder probe launched after bodies of
OL,4,Cman and woman found at house
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after the bodies of two
OL,8,Fpeople were found at a house in St
OL,9,FLeonards, East Sussex.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to an address in
OL,12,FSeven Acre Close shortly after 4.30am
OL,13,Fafter a man and a woman were reported
OL,14,Fto have been injured.
OL,16,FThe bodies of a 66-year-old man and a
OL,17,F46-year-old woman were found inside
OL,18,Fthe address.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
