OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782843506
OL,3,CMurder probe launched after bodies of
OL,4,Cman and woman found at house
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Jay Mendis-
OL,7,FGunasekera said: "This is a tragic
OL,8,Floss of life and our thoughts are with
OL,9,Fthe victims and their families and
OL,10,Ffriends at this very difficult time.
OL,12,F"We have arrested a 58-year-old man on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of the murder of a man and a
OL,14,Fwoman, and he remains in custody at
OL,15,Fthis time.
OL,26,@oD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
