PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782843506
OL,3,CMurder probe launched after bodies of
OL,4,Cman and woman found at house
OL,6,F"This is a fast-moving investigation
OL,7,Fas we seek to understand the wider
OL,8,Fcircumstances of what happened. It has
OL,9,Fbeen established that the suspect and
OL,10,Fvictims were known to each other and
OL,11,Fwe are not looking for anyone else at
OL,12,Fthis stage in connection with this.
OL,14,F"There will be an increased police
OL,15,Fpresence in the area while we complete
OL,16,Fenquiries.
